channel.title: Help getting server online
channel.description:
I went to play my server (317) and it said it isn't online but I had the 'runserver.bat' open. What could be wrong?
Also the compiler and runserver.bat when I open it, says the name of the Source I downloaded. Could I change that to the name of my server? Not really important, just wondering.
Thanks. :)
